{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_06_01",
  "title": "小美山愛 1話 やりとげてみせます！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyo_lessonstudio",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "愛、レッスンの調子はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ how's the lesson going?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん！　お疲れ様です\n今ちょうど一区切りついたところです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san! Good work.\nI just finished a section.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5492061933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、次の仕事の打ち合わせをするから\n着替えたら会議室に来てくれるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ I'll schedule the next job meeting‚\ncan you come to the conference room after changing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4000005245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "あのお話、決まったんですね！\n着替えてすぐに行きます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ the talk is settled‚ right!\nI'll change right away and come!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.6796825727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、せっかくならあの衣装に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ by the way‚ why not wear that outfit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.7130159061,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4220.317427199998,
          "startTime": 23.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.7130159061
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.9463492394
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせしました、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here I am‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7463492394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、早かったな……って\nなんでもう、その衣装を着てるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you're early… Wait‚\nwhy are you wearing that outfit already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3666662375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.0917453449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "次のお仕事は、この衣装で出ますから\n今のうちに慣れておこうと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll be wearing this outfit for the next job.\nI wanted to get used to it beforehand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7584120115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.1917468708
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "どうですか？　似合ってますか？\n私、かっこいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How does it look? Do I look good?\nDo I look cool?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1917468708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.5917468708
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、似合ってるしかっこいいぞ\nLizNoirのイメージにぴったりだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ you look good‚ and you're cool.\nIt suits LizNoir's image perfectly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4666677634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.9277103743
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "ですよね？　ですよね！？\n私、この衣装だと凄く強くなれる気がするんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right? Right!?\nI feel like I can be really strong in this outfit!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5610437077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.3943798384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、今回は大分気合いが入ってるみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But seriously‚ you seem quite motivated this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3943798384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、毎週観てるWeb番組でしたから\nいつか出てみたいな～って思ってたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ I've been watching this web show every week.\nI've always wanted to be on it someday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7341994287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.9008660954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "音楽系バラエティで、ミニゲームが熱いんですよね\n一番になるとアピールタイムがもらえちゃうっていう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a music variety show with exciting mini-games.\nIf you win‚ you get an appeal time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9008660954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.9341994287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirのライブが近いですし\nここで勝って、ちゃんと告知しないと……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir's live is coming up.\nIf we win here‚ we have to promote it properly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.2341994287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.567532762
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、でもあまり気負い過ぎないようにな\n前もソロの仕事で大分緊張していたようだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ but don't be too nervous.\nYou seemed quite tense during your solo work before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.4000049114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です！　この衣装に負けないくらい\nかっこよくかちゅやくしましゅから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay! I'll be cool and confident\nin this outfit!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.3271926564
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……ま、まぁほら、俺も同行するから\n今からそんなに緊張しなくて大丈夫だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ I'll be with you too‚\nso don't get too nervous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.5666715781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、同行してもらえるんですか！？\n今、とってもお忙しいって聞いてますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ you'll be coming with me!?\nBut I heard you're really busy right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9244030637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.4244040809
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "気にしなくていい。収録中はそばにいるよ\nそれが俺の仕事だからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry about it. I'll be by your side during the recording.\nThat's my job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.90000542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.1685535116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "……い、いえいえいえいえ！　大丈夫です！\n一人で行ってきますよ！　ご心配なさらず！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…N-no‚ no‚ no‚ no! I'm fine!\nI'll go by myself! Don't worry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5685535116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.0352201782
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "いつも観てる番組ですから雰囲気も分かりますし\nリズノワの一人として立派にやり遂げてみせます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I always watch the show‚ so I know the atmosphere‚ and\nI'll accomplish it splendidly as one of LizNoir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5352201782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "だから気負わなくていいって\n俺も無理している訳じゃないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So don't worry about it.\nI'm not pushing myself either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.80000542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.1743813518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫ですよっ！\nまかちぇてくだちゃいっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm okay!\nJust leave it to me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8410480185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.6410480185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
